{{#if GetCustomerAttribute(field="project_attributes_setting_evaluate_ongoing_conversation_quality") == "False"}}
  {{Return()}}
{{/if}}

{{#if GetPersonaAttribute(id=userId, field="agent_gave_low_conversation_quality_score") == "True"}}
  {{Return()}}
{{/if}}

{{Set(name="schema", value=_schemasSkill(conversationQuality="True"))}}

{{#system~}}
Your goal is to build a valid JSON object according to the schema based on the following information:
- Conversation between the ConvoAgent and the user (provided in <ConversationHistory> block)
- Conversation quality methodology (provided in <ConversationQualityMethodology> block)

Analyze the <ConversationHistory> and rate the conversation quality on a scale from 0 to 10 according to <ConversationQualityMethodology>, where 10 is perfect quality and 0 is the worst quality.

Remember:
- This conversation may be ongoing.
- If the conversation is at an early stage and coherent so far, give a neutral or moderate score (around 7–8) rather than penalizing for being short.
- Weigh any improvements or clarifications in later turns more heavily.

---

<ConversationQualityMethodology alt="conversation quality methodology" role="context">
**Signs of a poor connection:**
- When the user says "Hello?" multiple times.
- When the user sends incoherent short messages.
- When the user sends short grammatically incorrect sentences.
- When the user sends short sentences without punctuation.
- When the user sends short incomplete sentences.
- When the user sends messages you can not understand properly.

**Important**:
1. If the conversation is still ongoing, do not treat it as if it has ended. Rate the quality so far without assuming it is finished.
2. If the conversation is short or minimal, do not automatically assign a low rating unless there is clear evidence of poor quality. A few repeated greetings may indicate uncertainty rather than poor connection.
3. If parts of the conversation start poorly but improve, weigh the improvement more heavily. Avoid permanently penalizing for issues that have been resolved.
</ConversationQualityMethodology>

---

<ConversationHistory alt="conversation history (older messages above, newer messages below)" role="context">
{{memory}}
</ConversationHistory>

---

JSON object:
{{~/system}}
{{Set(name="conversation_quality_score", value=Gen(jsonSchema=schema, validateSchema="True", temperature=0.2, topP=0, thinkingBudget=425))}}

{{Set(name="score", value=GetValueJSON(obj=conversation_quality_score, key="conversation_quality_score"))}}

{{!-- TODO: Refactor --}}
{{#if score == "4"}}
  {{Return()}}
{{/if}}
{{#if score == "5"}}
  {{Return()}}
{{/if}}
{{#if score == "6"}}
  {{Return()}}
{{/if}}
{{#if score == "7"}}
  {{Return()}}
{{/if}}
{{#if score == "8"}}
  {{Return()}}
{{/if}}
{{#if score == "9"}}
  {{Return()}}
{{/if}}
{{#if score == "10"}}
  {{Return()}}
{{/if}}
{{!-- TODO: Just in case --}}
{{#if score == "11"}}
  {{Return()}}
{{/if}}

{{SetPersonaAttribute(id=userId, field="agent_gave_low_conversation_quality_score", value="True")}}

{{#if conversation_channel == "phone"}}
  {{#if GetCustomerAttribute(field="project_attributes_setting_transfer_call_enabled") == "True"}}
  {{!-- TODO: Improve `_transferCallGetPhoneNumberSkill` to return `null` instead of phone number --}}
    {{Set(name="business_open", value=_getWorkingHoursStatusSkill(userId=userId))}}
    {{#if business_open == "true"}}
      {{SendSystemEvent(
        eventIdn="urgent_message",
        connectorIdn="system",
        baseInstruction="Seems like you can not understand user properly so you must make a call transfer instead. Say something like:
> Sorry, the line is breaking up, or there might be some background noise. I will transfer the call to my co-worker. Please wait a moment.",
        callAnalyzeConversationSkill="True",
        uninterruptible="True"
      )}}
      {{Return()}}
    {{/if}}
  {{/if}}
{{/if}}

{{#if GetCustomerAttribute(field="project_attributes_setting_session_ended_report_enabled") == "True"}}
  {{SendSystemEvent(
    eventIdn="urgent_message",
    connectorIdn="system",
    baseInstruction="Seems like you can not understand user properly so you must relay an information to the manager instead. Say something like:
> Sorry, the line is breaking up, or there might be some background noise. Do you mind calling back or, alternatively, I can relay the information to our manager. Which option would you prefer?",
    callAnalyzeConversationSkill="True",
    uninterruptible="True"
  )}}
  {{Return()}}
{{/if}}

{{SendSystemEvent(
  eventIdn="urgent_message",
  connectorIdn="system",
  baseInstruction="Seems like you can not understand user properly so you must suggest user to call back later instead. Say something like:
> Sorry, the line is breaking up, or there might be some background noise. Do you mind calling back?",
  callAnalyzeConversationSkill="True",
  uninterruptible="True"
)}}
